description:
Minazuki Kashou is the protagonist of the Nekopara series and older brother of Shigure.
A patissier at Patisserie Soleil who left his home where his parents ran a Japanese confectionery to pursue his own dream. Applies himself so earnestly and thoroughly that his job and hobbies might as well be one and the same. Yet appealing to his humanity is all too easy, and he can`t help pampering the catgirls.
name: Minazuki Kashou
